# Generated benchmark outputs and temporary reports.
# Curated, version-controlled fixtures live under doc-benchmark/data/;
# everything below is scratch produced by CLI runs and must not be committed.
# The benchmark now lives in a subdirectory of the umbrella repo, so these are
# anchored to doc-benchmark/ (anchoring also keeps them from matching the
# curated data/<name>/ dirs, which share names like baselines/ and answers/).
/doc-benchmark/results/
/doc-benchmark/reports/
/doc-benchmark/dashboard.json
/doc-benchmark/jobs.json
/doc-benchmark/cr.md
/doc-benchmark/docs-quality-report/
/doc-benchmark/context7_comparison_results.json
*.log
*.tar.gz

# Default CLI output locations (curated copies are kept under data/).
/doc-benchmark/answers/
/doc-benchmark/eval/
/doc-benchmark/questions/
/doc-benchmark/personas/
/doc-benchmark/baselines/

